The paper also discusses the use of game theory to make machine learning algorithms more robust against adversarial attacks, which suggests that it could also belong to the cs.LG (Machine Learning) sub-category. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of deep learning techniques, which suggests that it could also belong to the cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of computer vision techniques, which suggests that it could belong to the cs.CV (Computer Vision) sub-category. Finally, the paper discusses the challenges and open problems in this area, which suggests that it could also belong to the cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) sub-category.
